entry.title: Cacomantis flabelliformis, Ptilotula penicillata
entry.content: This is a mexican standoff. The fan-tailed cuckoo is trying to lay an egg in the white plumed honeyeaters nest. If it succeeds that honeyeater will incubate and raise it as her own.
